annotationA: Early girl, isoform A; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity; acid-amino acid ligase activity; zinc ion binding; myosin binding; protein tag. It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of meiotic cell cycle; protein polyubiquitination
annotationB: Ubiquitin specific protease 8 is a protease involved in protein deubiquitination. It contributes to the integrity of ESCRT sorting machinery and the regulation of Hedgehog and Wingless signaling pathways; Belongs to the peptidase C19 family
